<p>ACT Responsable is an association that identifies and brings together the best committed advertisements around the world in order to raise awareness of major issues (solidarity, environment, human rights and education). The objective was to take care of the redesign of the French site, focused on the actions carried out by ACT Responsable, that is to say exhibitions, interventions in the school environment or the NG'Ad club</p>
        
